item.title: Repository - File page
item.description: JSON Object Types RepoFilePage js file example // Main object for the page type RepoFilePage{ fileName: string; grade: Grade; sourceCode: string; summary: FileSummary; fileWarning: FileWarning; } Subtypes type FileSummary{ stepMetric: StepMetric[]; } type Grade = "A" | "B" | "C" | "D" Keys fileType list of file types available here This will be determined by file extension in the future. Link to type references File/LineWarning for type FileWarning StepMetric NOTE any multiline string must be inside `` like example below
